{"tid":1589224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[去上水] 立場Live : 陳伯一個人去上水警署聲援被打男義工","createTime":"2019-09-23T07:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T08:14:37.000Z","uid":22556,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f75bdc1ff240f3223ae9da1d327435f540aebc44","tid":1589224,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:47:48.000Z","msg":"「守護孩子行動」成員前晚（9月21日）於元朗鳳攸北街被捕及被控以襲警。從網上片段可見，「守護孩子」男義工被帶到後巷，懷疑遭警察包圍毆打，有警察腳踢已經被制伏、沒有反抗能力的被捕者，樓上有街坊以手機拍下這一幕，有人大叫：「唔好打呀，阿Sir 停手！影住你呀！」數名警察紛紛以強光照向樓上的街坊，似是意圖阻止街坊拍攝。今日有消息指這名被警員在後巷腳踢毆打的男義工已出院，被帶到上水警署，守護孩子成員、曾經絕食的73歲陳伯擔心男義工情況，下午到上水警署外聲援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/1177688509084747?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F1177688509084747%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK6%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=a16620c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/1177688509084747?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"a7875b864aafbb666aa801f21adf39470325ccab","tid":1589224,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"0e85ce5cb1aa3d3f25058b70d44029c173fc44f4","tid":1589224,"uid":96852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e0c4dc76829af88462881872c73256666856156c","tid":1589224,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:50:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9415e32aa5c87a012572583cb88f570eae46ee4","tid":1589224,"uid":264308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face